{%- comment -%}
Shopify Storefront Custom CSS Limitations
1. Hard Character Limits
Section-Level: Max 500 characters (spaces/breaks included).
Theme-Level: Max 1500 characters.
Note: Code must often be minified to fit; extensive styling should move to theme assets.

2. Syntax Restrictions
No SCSS/Sass: Nesting is not supported (e.g., parent { child { ... } } is invalid). You must use standard CSS.
Restricted At-Rules: @import, @charset, and @namespace are prohibited.
Allowed At-Rules: @media, @container, @layer, and @supports work as expected.

3. Scoping & Selectors
The selector Keyword: Use selector { ... } to target the specific section wrapper dynamically.
Isolation: You cannot style elements outside the current section (e.g., cannot style the Header from a Product Section).
No Checkout Access: Custom CSS fields do not render on the Checkout page (requires Shopify Plus + Checkout Extensibility).

4. Known Technical Conflicts
JSON/Content Bug: Using the content property with quotes (e.g., content: ""; for pseudo-elements) often breaks the JSON save file.
Workaround: Move code utilizing ::before/::after to the main stylesheet (base.css / theme.css).

For full Custom CSS Limitations, please read the readme.md file
{%- endcomment -%}


/*     Collapsible Content   */
/* Add a black background to the header */
.collapsible-content__header {
  background-color: #000000;
  padding-top: 15px;
  padding-bottom: 15px;
} /* Make the heading text white and remove its bottom margin */
.collapsible-content__heading {
  color: #ffffff;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

/*   Multicolumn Section for Icons  */
/* --- Make images smaller and centered --- */
.multicolumn-card__image-wrapper {
  max-width: 80px; /* Adjust this value to make icons bigger or smaller */
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  margin-bottom: 0px;
} /* --- Make images circular --- */
.multicolumn-card__image {
  border-radius: 10%;
} /* --- Change column text color to black --- */
.multicolumn-card__info 3,
.multicolumn-card__info .rte {
  color: #000000;
}
.multicolumn-card__info {
  color: #000000;
}
.h2 {
  text-align: center;
}
.inline-richtext h2 {
  text-align: center;
}

/*   Multicolumn Section for Days Breakdown   */
/* Make the entire group of columns narrower and centered */
.multicolumn-list {
  max-width: 100rem; /* Adjust this value to make the section wider or narrower */
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
} /* Force the background of each column to be white */
.multicolumn-card__info {
  background-color: #ffffff;
}

/*   Multicolumn Section for CTA for other Itins   */
.link {
  padding: 10px;
  padding-left: 15px;
  background-color: #ff0000;
  color: #ffffff;
}

/*   Multicolumn Section for 3 simple steps   */
/* Style the main heading container */
.multicolumn__title {
  background-color: #000000;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center !important;
} /* Change the heading text to white */
.multicolumn__title .title {
  color: #ffffff;
} /* Keep the text in the columns black */
.multicolumn-card__info {
  color: #000000;
}

/*   Multicolumn Section for Recommendations on Help Hub   */
.multicolumn-card__image {
  border-radius: 15px;
}
.multicolumn-list {
  justify-content: center;
}

/*   Tab-with-content for Take a Peak section   */
.tabs-with-content__tab-button {
  text-transform: none;
}

/*   Video with Text on help hub   */
.button {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}
